{
  "texts": [
    "We then manually label the data and select prompts that perform well.",
    "The resultant prompts are used to generate more data, which are again manually labelled.",
    "The labeled data can be used as seeds for the next round of data generation.",
    "This process is repeated several times.",
    "Finally, we collected a high-quality optimization training dataset with total 15k instances in English and Chinese."
  ]
}